# AI Configuration (Add these to your .env file)

# Option 1: OpenAI (Recommended)
# Get your API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key-here

# Option 2: Google Gemini (Alternative)
# Get your API key from: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key-here

# Note: Only one API key is required. OpenAI will be used if both are configured.
# If neither is configured, the system will use mock AI responses.

# Pricing (as of 2024):
# - OpenAI GPT-3.5-Turbo: ~$0.002 per 1K tokens
# - Google Gemini Pro: Free tier available, then pay-as-you-go
